{"tid":2267707,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生被控肩撞警長阻追犯 辯方指警長意外碰撞後歸咎被告","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T09:45:41.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a34616c52f7928b8d9b2b5562c1c77960bba188e","tid":2267707,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"公開大學男生被指去年9月在深水涉用膊頭撞向一名警長，阻礙警長追捕疑犯。男生否認阻差辦公罪，案件今開審。辯方指事件純屬意外，實情是警長追捕疑犯時不小心撞到被告，然後一度舉起拳頭，兇惡地質問：「做咩撞我？」然後<span class=\"red\">警長放棄追捕，將責任推到被告身上</span>。警長全部不同意。被告自辯稱，當時警長表現兇惡，並舉起左手「好似想打我咁」，他因感到害怕才逃跑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方則指出，黃追捕綠衣男途中，有一輛輕型貨車停泊在南昌街路邊，並一度阻擋黃的視線。黃否認，稱<span class=\"red\">視線從沒離開綠衣男</span>。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指，當時被告正過馬路，從沒向綠衣男叫「快啲走」，亦沒用膊頭撞向黃，反而是被黃不小心撞到；黃不同意。辯方又指，案發時被告並沒向前衝；黃同意，指被告僅是上身擺動。"},{"pid":"62c00c5d2c3b487a68accf41c0c991646c4f4fb9","tid":2267707,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/CRLAZCDSWRH4VJR5IL45HPDQYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FCRLAZCDSWRH4VJR5IL45HPDQYU%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=f5afc3cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FCRLAZCDSWRH4VJR5IL45HPDQYU%2F&h=93428f42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/CRLAZCDSWRH4VJR5IL45HPDQYU/</a>"},{"pid":"aef65751f7f498159a37360d09a580d01769fe54","tid":2267707,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"呢啲要睇有冇片<br />\n無片嘅話 = 100% 入"},{"pid":"c02b33f6aa4fbda5aa51969b68d034d165fadb71","tid":2267707,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ea01cda440c8570a0c96948fe7d9011f75dc40","tid":2267707,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":